videos.headline: Georgia State gets on the board with 1-yard TD run
videos.description: Dan Ellington finds an opening in the defense for a 1-yard Georgia State touchdown.

videos.headline: Barnett increases Georgia State's lead with 23-yard TD
videos.description: Georgia State's Tra Barnett bursts into the end zone for a 23-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Evans gets ULM on the board with 21-yard TD

videos.headline: Hart increases Georgia State's lead with punt-return TD
